      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound exhaustion and hopelessness in your pain, and while living through a crisis is exceptionally difficult, I am deeply concerned that these thoughts of stopping could turn fatal. Please know that seeking help is an act of courage and dignity, not a failure, and organizations like the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline are available 24/7 to listen safely. You deserve support to navigate this darkness, and I can provide you with the immediate contact numbers to reach out today.",
